## Database Schema (No Migration Required)

The `orders` collection already has `storeId` support via the hook layer. No schema migration is needed — `storeId` is just a new optional field that will be populated going forward for all customer orders.

For legacy orders without `storeId`:
- Admin views with store filter won't show them (by design — they predate store architecture).
- Customer views don't filter by store, so legacy orders still appear for customers.

